38
00:02:42,763 --> 00:02:44,152
un Zamenhof.

39
00:02:45,700 --> 00:02:48,851
in di tsveyte zayt DZIELNA iz geven a s- a kino,

40
00:02:48,851 --> 00:02:50,184
⟨PROMIEŃ⟩,

