52
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:31,054
neyn. ikh hob ongehoybn di yidishe folk-shul

53
00:03:31,054 --> 00:03:35,573
fun di Tsisho-organizatsye, Tsentrale Yidishe Shul-Organizatsye.

54
00:03:35,573 --> 00:03:38,906
di dozike shuln zenen geven oysshlislekh

55
00:03:38,906 --> 00:03:41,221
in yidish.

56
00:03:41,221 --> 00:03:42,776
oyser dem,

57
00:03:42,776 --> 00:03:47,685
hot, iz geven tsvey sho poylish, poylishe geshikhte, literatur,

58
00:03:47,685 --> 00:03:49,110
un di shprakh.

59
00:03:49,110 --> 00:03:51,240
vayl di makht-organen

60
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:55,425
hobn zeyer shtark akhtung gegebn oyf di dozike shuln

61
00:03:55,425 --> 00:03:58,981
vayl zey zenen geven, azoy tsu zogn,

62
00:03:58,981 --> 00:04:01,777
sotsyalistishe, veltlekhe shuln.

63
00:04:01,777 --> 00:04:04,185
un oyser dem in di yidishe shprakh,

64
00:04:04,185 --> 00:04:06,555
vos a sakh kenen es nisht farshteyn,

65
00:04:06,555 --> 00:04:11,221
az in di dozike shprakh zenen geven ale kegnshtandn.

66
00:04:11,221 --> 00:04:15,258
matematik, algebre, geshikhte,

67
00:04:15,258 --> 00:04:18,814
 geshikhte, natur-visnshaft, geografye,

68
00:04:18,814 --> 00:04:20,017
alts in yidish.

69
00:04:20,017 --> 00:04:20,797
alts in yidish.

70
00:04:20,742 --> 00:04:21,487
yo.

71
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:24,943
un,

