00:04:24,943 --> 00:04:27,131
ir zent geven,

73
00:04:27,131 --> 00:04:29,703
farshtendlekh nisht in a religyeze shtub.

74
00:04:29,703 --> 00:04:30,985
di shtub iz nisht geven...

75
00:04:30,296 --> 00:04:34,819
di shtub iz nisht geven religyez. di umgebung

76
00:04:34,819 --> 00:04:37,370
iz mer geven traditsyonel.

77
00:04:37,370 --> 00:04:41,431
shabes iz geven shabes, yontoyvim zenen geven yontoyvim.

78
00:04:41,431 --> 00:04:47,018
der tate fun onhoyb flegt geyn in shul arayn, in der fri shabes tsum davenen.

79
00:04:47,018 --> 00:04:48,827
flegt er undz mitnemen,

80
00:04:48,827 --> 00:04:50,814
di klenere kinder.

81
00:04:50,814 --> 00:04:56,055
ober di shamosim hobn gegat gebrente tsores, flegn zey undz aroysyogn fun shul.

82
00:04:56,055 --> 00:05:02,267
iz, bikhlal in ayer shtub hot men gefayert di yomim-toyvim?

83
00:05:01,536 --> 00:05:05,777
yo, s'iz, azoy vi tsu zogn, s'iz geven azoy vi obligatorish.

84
00:05:05,777 --> 00:05:10,054
m'hot nisht gekent zayn in di dortike umgebung

85
00:05:10,054 --> 00:05:14,017
in gantsn fray, zikh firn azoy vi eyner vil.

86
00:05:14,017 --> 00:05:16,444
 vos heyst me hot nisht gekent?

87
00:05:16,444 --> 00:05:17,906
lemoshl

88
00:05:17,906 --> 00:05:21,129
haltn ofn dem varshtat shabes.

89
00:05:21,129 --> 00:05:25,227
oder yontoyvim ven me tor nisht arbetn, oder geyn in shule ven...

90
00:05:25,758 --> 00:05:26,517
di gan-

91
00:05:25,816 --> 00:05:28,407
ober, ober bay zikh in der heym?

92
00:05:27,925 --> 00:05:31,362
bay zikh in der heym ken yeder eyner tun vos er vil.

93
00:05:31,362 --> 00:05:33,357
ober me darf zikh a bisl

94
00:05:33,357 --> 00:05:37,000
oykhet nemen a bisl respekt tsulib di shkheynim.

95
00:05:39,036 --> 00:05:43,981
vi azoy iz geven dos yidishe lebn demolt in Varshe?

96
00:05:43,981 --> 00:05:49,466
dos yidishe lebn iz geven a zeyer filfarbik un a zeyer fulblutik lebn.

97
00:05:50,911 --> 00:06:00,018
oyser dem hobn oyf di yidishe gas geven alerley politishe parteyen,

98
00:06:00,018 --> 00:06:02,444
onheybndik afile in di religyeze,

99
00:06:02,444 --> 00:06:04,666
vos zey hobn gehat tsvey parteyen.

100
00:06:04,666 --> 00:06:06,277
di Agude,

101
00:06:06,277 --> 00:06:08,295
un p-, un Mizrokhi.

102
00:06:08,295 --> 00:06:10,504
Mizrokhi un Hapoyel-Hamizrokhi.

103
