yo.

105
00:06:13,944 --> 00:06:16,277
biz dem ekstrem links,

106
00:06:16,277 --> 00:06:18,184
un komunizm.

107
00:06:18,184 --> 00:06:22,203
tsienistishe organizatsyes, sotsyalistishe organizatsyes.

108
00:06:22,267 --> 00:06:23,205
ir zent geven

109
00:06:22,695 --> 00:06:24,056
profesyonele fareynen.

110
00:06:24,147 --> 00:06:26,851
eygene yidishe profesyonele fareynen.

111
00:06:26,851 --> 00:06:36,555
vayl der tsutrit fun di yidishe arbeter oyf gresere fabrikn iz geven kimat vi opgeshlosn.

112
00:06:36,555 --> 00:06:45,740
un di profesyonele fareynen... iz geven shtarke fareynen, un ⟨zey hobn arayngenumen⟩ dem grestn teyl di yidishe fakhn.

113
00:06:45,740 --> 00:06:47,444
metal,

114
00:06:47,444 --> 00:06:52,462
 nodl-industrye, ikh vil zogn, shnayderay, stolyeray.

115
00:06:52,462 --> 00:06:54,759
dos alts zaynen geven yidishe fakhn?

116
00:06:54,688 --> 00:06:55,647
yidishe fakhn.

117
00:06:57,369 --> 00:07:02,684
ir zent geven, ir hot balangt tsu epes a organizatsye?

118
00:07:02,684 --> 00:07:05,165
tsi ikh? yo.

119
00:07:03,463 --> 00:07:03,871
yo.

120
00:07:05,165 --> 00:07:08,129
onheybndik in shule shoyn

121
00:07:08,343 --> 00:07:11,332
di ekonomishe situatsye hot gevirkt

122
00:07:11,332 --> 00:07:17,629
az, zol ikh onheybn fun kindvayz oyf farnemen mit politik, iz di eybike frage: far vos?

123
00:07:17,629 --> 00:07:19,443
iz,

124
00:07:19,443 --> 00:07:23,369
fun onhoyb hob ikh gehert, s'heyst in di onfang-shule, in di folk-shule,

125
00:07:23,369 --> 00:07:28,073
hob ikh gehert tsu di komunistishe kinder-organizatsye, Pyoner.

126
00:07:28,073 --> 00:07:34,443
a bisl di romantik, a bisl vegn di umlegalkeyt, ober shpeter

127
00:07:34,443 --> 00:07:39,647
mer-veyniker in a tsvey yor arum bin ikh aribergeganen in Skif, Sotsyalistisher Kinder-Farband.

128
00:07:39,647 --> 00:07:42,906
dos hot gehert tsu di bundishe organizatsyes.

129
00:07:42,906 --> 00:07:47,814
in vos zaynen bashtanen di di zakhn vos ir hot g- oyfgetun, vos ir hot getun?

130
00:07:47,814 --> 00:07:50,795
oyfgetun, nisht mir hobn oyfgetun.

131
00:07:50,795 --> 00:07:53,369
nor me hot far undz oyfgetun,

132
00:07:53,369 --> 00:07:56,573
vayl me hot undz aroysgeshlept fun di gas.

133
00:07:57,073 --> 00:08:03,944
m'hot undz gevizn, gelernt a naye velt. a frayere velt.

134
00:08:03,944 --> 00:08:06,407
organizirn,

135
00:08:06,407 --> 00:08:10,370
lomir zogn, kinder-kolonyes, bay undz hot dos geheysn kinder-lagern.

136
00:08:10,370 --> 00:08:13,147
fun aroysforn far tsvey vokhn

137
00:08:13,147 --> 00:08:16,647
in di velder noent fun taykh,

138
00:08:16,647 --> 00:08:18,444
azoy tsu zogn,

139
00:08:18,444 --> 00:08:19,417
skoytn.

140
00:08:20,911 --> 00:08:25,055
me flegt aroysforn, me flegt zikh oyfshteln aleyn di getseltn,

141
00:08:25,055 --> 00:08:26,907
a republik, a gantse republik.

142
00:08:26,907 --> 00:08:30,129
vifl zent ir alt geven demolt?

143
00:08:30,129 --> 00:08:34,332
kh'bin alt geven tsvelef yor, fun tsvelef yor hob ikh ongehoybn tsu forn.

144
00:08:34,332 --> 00:08:36,406
bekhinem iz es nisht geven.

145
00:08:37,147 --> 00:08:41,906
ober s'iz geven zeyer a groyse shtitsung, me darf dos untershtraykhn.

146
00:08:41,906 --> 00:08:44,776
farn gantsn gezelshaft ⟨vos hot gelebt⟩ in Poyln.

147
00:08:44,776 --> 00:08:49,763
di shtitser fun yidishn arbeter-komitet, fun Nord-Amerike, fun JOINT,

148
00:08:49,763 --> 00:08:54,194
un fun yidishn natsyonaln arbeter-komitet.

149
00:08:54,194 --> 00:08:59,888
ober me hot shtendik gedarft hobn, azoy tsu zogn, a por eygene zlotes.

150
00:08:59,888 --> 00:09:02,795
