155
00:09:11,406 --> 00:09:13,387
..

156
00:09:13,387 --> 00:09:15,054
vos shayekh, dem tog vi a...

157
00:09:14,507 --> 00:09:17,408
a tog, a tog, vi a tog, a geveynlekhn tog.

158
00:09:16,541 --> 00:09:20,017
a geveynlekher tog iz geven, zeyer eynfakh.

159
00:09:20,017 --> 00:09:22,887
in der fri in shule...

160
00:09:22,887 --> 00:09:27,499
di shule iz merstn teyl geven zeks un zibn sho,

161
00:09:27,499 --> 00:09:31,758
vayl tsulib di poylishe shprakh zenen tsugeganen tsvey sho,

162
00:09:31,758 --> 00:09:33,573
mer.

163
00:09:33,573 --> 00:09:35,795
nokhn aheymkumen fun di shule

164
00:09:35,795 --> 00:09:38,502
hot men gedarft makhn di lektsyes.

165
00:09:38,502 --> 00:09:41,055
kh'vil zogn, az me hot nokh gedarft lernen.

166
00:09:41,055 --> 00:09:44,777
shpeter zenen mir a bisl arumgelofn di gas, ober dem merstn teyl,

167
00:09:44,777 --> 00:09:51,313
ikh perzenlekh, dem merstn teyl iz mir geven interesant literatur, kh'vil zogn, bikher.

168
00:09:51,313 --> 00:09:53,999
geleyent, geleyent on a shier.

169
00:09:53,999 --> 00:09:57,628
un dokh, ikh vil dokh es untershtraykhn, vayl a sakh veysn nisht:

170
00:09:57,628 --> 00:09:59,846
di gantse velt-literatur

171
00:09:59,846 --> 00:10:01,735
iz geven ibergezetst in yidish.

172
00:10:01,962 --> 00:10:03,740
ir hot geleyent nor yidish?

173
