der tsarisher kuryer fun JULES VERNE,

182
00:10:26,204 --> 00:10:29,346
der fuftsn-yeriker kapitan,

183
00:10:29,346 --> 00:10:32,785
VICTOR HUGO, LES MISERABLES, MISERABLES.

