189
00:10:46,597 --> 00:10:51,110
lomir zogn, fun onhoyb iz nisht geven keyn antisemit- vos,

190
00:10:51,110 --> 00:10:55,555
me zol filn, ober mitn loyf, funem oyfkum funem natsizm,

191
00:10:55,555 --> 00:10:57,239
iz, kh'vil zogn,

192
00:10:57,239 --> 00:10:58,906
toyznt nayn hundert draysik,

193
00:10:58,906 --> 00:11:02,666
fun a- toyznt nayn hundert draysik biz nayn un draysik

194
00:11:02,666 --> 00:11:06,536
hot zikh unter der virkung fun Daytshland geshtarkt der poylisher

195
00:11:06,536 --> 00:11:07,962
antisemitizm.

196
00:11:07,962 --> 00:11:09,629
far dem nisht?

197
00:11:09,629 --> 00:11:13,981
far dem iz nisht geven keyn

198
00:11:13,981 --> 00:11:17,851
vi zol ikh dos oysdrikn? far dem iz nisht geven azoy tsu zogn,

199
00:11:17,851 --> 00:11:21,665
k'aza shtrenger oder k'aza

200
00:11:21,665 --> 00:11:26,424
zoologisher antisemitizm.

201
00:11:26,424 --> 00:11:29,850
un der zoologisher ba-, bay dem bashteyt in dem

202
00:11:29,850 --> 00:11:32,943
ober di halb-fashistishe poylishe regirung

203
00:11:32,943 --> 00:11:36,091
iz geven maskem

204
00:11:36,091 --> 00:11:43,147
oyf tsu, oyf tsu aropniderikn dem nivo, oder aropdrikn dem ekonomishn nivo.

205
00:11:43,147 --> 00:11:47,480
vayl fun onhoyb iz geven der ekonomisher antisemitizm,

206
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:50,721
bashrenkung oyfn yidishn handl, oyf yidisher arbet.

207
00:11:50,721 --> 00:11:55,350
shpeter iz tsugekumen shoyn der fizisher antisemitizm

208
00:11:55,350 --> 00:11:59,666
fun onfaln direkt oyf yidn.

209
00:11:59,666 --> 00:12:02,281
