yidn furmanes,

216
00:12:23,036 --> 00:12:25,962
yidn katsovim, s'heyst, fleysh-arbeter.

217
00:12:25,962 --> 00:12:26,779
nu?

218
00:12:26,818 --> 00:12:31,110
un s'iz geven, iz gevorn organizirt az in di erter

219
00:12:31,110 --> 00:12:33,952
⟨hot men⟩ merstn teyl, flegn zey iberfaln in Krashinski's gortn.

220
00:12:33,952 --> 00:12:35,541
s'iz geven der gortn

221
00:12:35,541 --> 00:12:39,907
kimat a yidisher gortn, vayl s'iz gelign in di yidishe gegnt.

222
00:12:39,907 --> 00:12:42,295
geshafn zelbshuts-grupn,

223
00:12:42,295 --> 00:12:44,147
un flegt opentfern

224
00:12:44,147 --> 00:12:46,758
geshleg mit geshleg.

225
00:12:46,758 --> 00:12:51,628
in di gegnt fun Krokhmalne-gas, vos iz azoy bakant mitn Krokhmalner pletsl,

226
00:12:51,628 --> 00:12:53,165
dort iz shtendik

227
00:12:53,165 --> 00:12:56,591
flegn zey avekgeyn mit tseblutikte kep.

228
00:12:56,591 --> 00:12:58,576
azoy...

229
00:12:58,576 --> 00:13:04,443
far, di gantse yugnt, s'heyst mayn yugnt, hobn eybik, fun di draysiker yorn

230
00:13:04,443 --> 00:13:08,166
iz shoyn dertsoygn gevorn oyf aktivn vidershtand

231
00:13:08,166 --> 00:13:10,462
un nisht oyf a pasivn vidershtand

232
00:13:10,462 --> 00:13:13,573
vi s'iz geven di meynung fun di religyeze krayzn.

233
00:13:13,573 --> 00:13:16,092
nisht antloyfn, tsurikgebn.

234
00:13:13,638 --> 00:13:14,393
ir ken-

235
00:13:16,092 --> 00:13:19,373
 me ken zogn az di gantse yugnt iz geven azoy?

236
00:13:19,073 --> 00:13:20,314
di gantse yugnt.

237
00:13:20,314 --> 00:13:21,676
di gantse yugnt?

238
00:13:20,876 --> 00:13:23,262
di gantse yugnt, oyser di religyeze.

239
00:13:25,303 --> 00:13:28,610
di tsienistishe, di HASHOMER-HATSAIR,

240
00:13:28,610 --> 00:13:31,017
di komunistishe, di sotsyalistishe.

241
00:13:31,017 --> 00:13:32,871
s'iz geven epes a min

242
00:13:32,443 --> 00:13:33,666
geven shtendik...

243
00:13:32,883 --> 00:13:36,499
kontakt tsvishn di bazundere organizatsyes?

244
00:13:34,684 --> 00:13:35,610
neyn.

245
00:13:36,323 --> 00:13:40,962
dos iz geven der eyntsiker kontakt, in diskusyes un in geshlegn.

246
00:13:40,962 --> 00:13:44,843
eyn grupe, vos ikh muz dermanen, vos mir hobn faynt gehat

247
00:13:44,843 --> 00:13:47,851
iz geven der BETAR, fun di revizyonistn.

248
00:13:47,851 --> 00:13:52,796
nisht, teyl mol, azoy vi me zogt, UNK ⟨sharfe⟩ ideologishe sikhsukhim.

249
00:13:52,796 --> 00:13:58,433
di problem iz geven, flegn aroyskumen broyne hemder mit shvartse binders, mit shvartse kravatn.

250
00:13:58,433 --> 00:14:01,120
un dos veyst men gants gut, az s'iz geven

251
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:06,832
der uniform fun di N.S.D.A.P. in Daytshland.

252
00:14:06,832 --> 00:14:10,758
un vi azoy hobn zey es gegebn tsu farshteyn?

253
00:14:10,758 --> 00:14:12,254
ikh veys,.

254
00:14:12,254 --> 00:14:17,166
vi azoy git men tsu farshteyn teyl mol a kegner? mit mit gutn? nisht.

255
00:14:17,166 --> 00:14:21,555
iz aropraysn di shvartse binder, oder tseraysn oyf im dos hemd.

256
00:14:21,555 --> 00:14:26,444
iz, ir vilt zogn az ir hot ge- gefilt az epes

257
00:14:26,444 --> 00:14:28,974
bayt zikh in di svive,

258
00:14:29,185 --> 00:14:31,518
in di draysiker yorn?

259
00:14:31,518 --> 00:14:33,792
avade, es bayt zikh tsum ergern.

260
00:14:33,792 --> 00:14:35,301
koydem iz geven

261
00:14:36,083 --> 00:14:36,790
ven hot ir...

262
00:14:36,422 --> 00:14:37,964
der ekonomisher krizis.

263
00:14:39,073 --> 00:14:42,184
in Poyln,

264
00:14:42,184 --> 00:14:44,795
Poyln iber hoypt, un yidn iber hoypt,

265
00:14:44,795 --> 00:14:45,760
bikhlal,

266
00:14:45,760 --> 00:14:49,314
hobn gezukht a veg tsu emigrirn.

267
00:14:49,314 --> 00:14:52,647
iz bay ale parteyen, aynshlislekh baym Bund,

268
00:14:52,647 --> 00:14:56,189
vern geshafn emigratsye-byuroen.

269
00:14:56,189 --> 00:15:02,425
vos, tsu makhn di ale farlaykhterungen vu meglekh, vu s- hot men gekent forn

270
00:15:02,425 --> 00:15:05,723
vayl di emigratsye keyn Yisroel iz geven bagrenetst.

271
00:15:05,723 --> 00:15:10,888
di emigratsye keyn Nord-Amerike, un Latayn-Amerikaner lender, iz gevorn bagrenetst.

272
00:15:10,888 --> 00:15:14,129
vu iz a meglekhkeyt hot men farbundn familyes.

273
00:15:14,129 --> 00:15:16,017
vil ikh zogn azoy: frier

274
00:15:16,017 --> 00:15:19,814
in di tsvontsiker yorn, ven s'iz geven frayer di emigratsye,

275
00:15:19,814 --> 00:15:23,054
az di dortike vos zey zenen avekgeforn frier zoln kenen

276
00:15:23,054 --> 00:15:25,203
aroysnemen familyes,

277
00:15:25,203 --> 00:15:27,981
kroyvim, ariber- ariberfirn

278
00:15:27,981 --> 00:15:31,851
fun di lender vu me hot gekent emigrirn.

279
00:15:32,295 --> 00:15:34,000
a sakh hobn emigrirt?

280
00:15:33,555 --> 00:15:35,073
yo.

281
00:15:34,929 --> 00:15:36,507
in di draysiker yorn

282
00:15:35,179 --> 00:15:39,851
vifl, ver, vifl es hot gekent, hot emigrirt.

283
00:15:39,851 --> 00:15:41,028
un...

284
00:15:40,462 --> 00:15:44,666
say tsulib di ekonomishe situatsye, un say tsulib di politishe situatsye.

285
00:15:44,666 --> 00:15:47,832
⟨az oyb in⟩ di draysiker yorn,

286
00:15:47,832 --> 00:15:50,406
zibn un draysik,

287
00:15:50,406 --> 00:15:53,425
hot gekent forkumen di pogromen

288
00:15:53,425 --> 00:15:58,055
oyf yidn in PRZYTYK, in Minsk-Mazovyetsk,

289
00:15:58,055 --> 00:16:04,703
bemeyle, un dos hot farshtarkt dem shtrom fun emigratsye.

290
00:16:04,703 --> 00:16:08,323
ir hot oykhet geklert in a gevisn moment tsu emigrirn?

291
00:16:07,935 --> 00:16:13,000
kh'vel aykh zogn, di geshikhte iz azoy. mayn foter, mayn tate

292
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:21,425
mit an eltern bruder, zenen gekumen keyn Argentine, zenen aroys fun Poyln, in toyznt nayn hundert nayn un tsvontsik.

293
00:16:21,425 --> 00:16:25,981
ober s'iz geven a groyse familye

294
00:16:25,981 --> 00:16:31,036
un di meglekhkeytn az er zol undz aribernemen iz nisht geven.

295
00:16:31,036 --> 00:16:38,018
iz der elterer bruder geblibn in Argentine, un er iz tsurikgekumen keyn Poyln in toyznt nayn hundert fir un draysik.

296
00:16:38,018 --> 00:16:40,240
ven er volt gekent geyn tsu fus,

297
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:42,999
megt ir zayn zikher, er volt tsurikgeganen keyn Argentine.

298
00:16:42,999 --> 00:16:46,888
ober s'iz shoyn geven farfaln.

299
00:16:46,888 --> 00:16:50,708
ven hot ir gefilt az se halt bay oysbrekhn a milkhome?

300
00:16:53,462 --> 00:16:55,979
gefilt hot men

301
00:16:56,869 --> 00:17:00,221
onheybndik fun di khoydesh oygust,

302
00:17:00,221 --> 00:17:02,685
yuni, yuli, oygust.

303
00:17:02,685 --> 00:17:06,092
hot men gefilt az s'ken kumen tsu a tsuzamenshtoys.

304
00:17:06,092 --> 00:17:07,944
funem nayn un draysikstn yor.

305
00:17:07,944 --> 00:17:10,129
nayn un draysikstn yor.

306
00:17:10,129 --> 00:17:16,203
ober dos vos s'hot derfirt tsu der milkhome, m'hot dershpirt az s'kumt di milkhome,

307
00:17:16,203 --> 00:17:20,666
iz geven der, di opmakh tsvishn Hitler un Stalin.

308
00:17:20,666 --> 00:17:22,458
dos iz geven fir teg,

309
00:17:22,458 --> 00:17:26,944
s'iz geven mit-, sof oygust, dakht zikh mir, in nayn un draysikstn yor

310
00:17:26,944 --> 00:17:30,684
un es heybt zikh on di mobilizatsye fun poylishn militer.

311
00:17:30,684 --> 00:17:36,925
vi azoy hot ir ongenumen dos, dem pakt tsvishn Hitler un Stalin?

312
00:17:36,925 --> 00:17:40,184
m'hot denstmol, ikh veys nisht,

313
00:17:40,184 --> 00:17:43,407
m'hot denstmol nisht geleygt oyf dem keyn groysn akht,

314
00:17:43,407 --> 00:17:47,314
vayl me hot nisht gevust in vos der pakt bashteyt.

315
00:17:47,314 --> 00:17:52,740
a pakt tsvishn tsvey melukhes, un kegnzaytlekhe melukhes,

316
00:17:52,740 --> 00:17:55,647
vegn frayndshaft un nisht-iberfaln,

317
00:17:55,647 --> 00:17:58,369
vayl s'iz geven ⟨dan⟩ UNK Frankraykh.

318
00:17:58,369 --> 00:18:06,462
Frankraykh un Rusland un Poyln veln shlisn a opmakh fun kegnzaytike hilf.

319
00:18:06,462 --> 00:18:15,443
ober in yenem moment hot zikh Sovyet-Rusland tsurikgetsoygn, geshlosn punkt farkert, a opmakh mit Hitler-Daytshland.

320
00:18:15,443 --> 00:18:20,628
vos iz geshen, vos gedenkt ir funem tog ven s'iz oysgebrokhn take di milkhome?

321
00:18:20,724 --> 00:18:22,851
di milkhome hot zikh ongehoybn

322
00:18:22,851 --> 00:18:28,336
bald mitn onfli fun daytshishe avyonen oyf Varshe.

323
00:18:28,336 --> 00:18:30,931
fun dem hob ikh gehat dervust in der fri.

324
00:18:30,931 --> 00:18:36,258
un far tog zenen daytshn ariber- ibergefaln Poyln.

325
00:18:36,258 --> 00:18:41,603
dos fartunklen, dos onnemen ale gever.

326
00:18:41,603 --> 00:18:47,296
ale geveynlekhe shuts-mitlen kegn luft-ongrifn.

327
00:18:47,296 --> 00:18:49,740
un mit dem hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome.

328
00:18:49,887 --> 00:18:53,690
vi azoy hot ir es dos durkhgelebt, vi a- vos hot ir gefilt?

329
00:18:52,185 --> 00:18:54,074
durkhgelebt, durkhgelebt?

330
00:18:54,074 --> 00:18:55,212
ir gedenkt?

331
00:18:55,212 --> 00:19:01,074
durkhgelebt hot men oyf dem, ikh perzenlekh,

332
00:19:01,074 --> 00:19:03,462
az s'vet kumen mayn tsayt,

333
00:19:03,462 --> 00:19:06,262
vayl ikh bin denstmol alt geven zekhtsn, zibetsn yor,

334
00:19:06,262 --> 00:19:10,351
⟨s'vet kumen⟩ mayn tsayt geyn kemfn in der armey.

335
00:19:10,351 --> 00:19:12,981
ikh zog nisht azoy letoyves

336
00:19:12,981 --> 00:19:16,370
Poyln, ikh vil,

337
00:19:16,370 --> 00:19:20,740
kh'muz shlogn dem natsi, shlogn di daytshn.

338
00:19:20,740 --> 00:19:24,314
vayl di poylishe yugnt, kh'hob frier nisht ge-, kh'hob nisht tsugegebn,

339
00:19:24,314 --> 00:19:29,573
ir hot gefregt vegn di poy-, vegn di yugnt, di yidishe yugnt in Poyln.

340
00:19:29,573 --> 00:19:32,610
fun Poyln zenen a sakh UNK yugntlekhe avek.

341
00:19:32,610 --> 00:19:35,110
ven es iz geven der birger-krig in Shpanye.

342
00:19:35,110 --> 00:19:37,610
zeks un draysik, nayn un draysik.

343
00:19:37,610 --> 00:19:41,425
zikh ongeshlosn in di internatsyonale brigades

344
00:19:41,425 --> 00:19:43,313
un aynshlislekh iz geven

345
00:19:43,313 --> 00:19:45,425
di yidishe kamfs-,

346
00:19:45,425 --> 00:19:49,147
kamfs-brigade, Botvinik.

347
00:19:49,147 --> 00:19:54,388
a sakh hobn epes, ayere khaveyrim, oder ayere bakante hobn zikh ayngesh-

348
00:19:53,036 --> 00:19:56,080
 khaveyrim nisht, ober bakante yo.

349
00:19:58,128 --> 00:20:00,332
bakante yugntlekhe, yo.

350
00:20:00,332 --> 00:20:01,999
un nakher zaynen zey tsurikgekumen?

351
00:20:01,999 --> 00:20:02,591
?

352
00:20:02,506 --> 00:20:06,735
zey zaynen tsurikgekumen? gedenkt nit...

353
00:20:05,703 --> 00:20:08,184
vintsik.

354
00:20:08,220 --> 00:20:12,629
nu, iz, haltn mir baym oysbrokh fun der milkhome.

355
00:20:12,629 --> 00:20:18,814
 dos fun ershtn, bald fun onhoyb, zenen di gesheenishn geganen zeyer shnel.

356
00:20:18,814 --> 00:20:21,477
far di ongrif fun di daytshn

357
00:20:21,477 --> 00:20:24,421
in Poyln hobn zey ongevendet, nokh Shpanye,

358
00:20:24,421 --> 00:20:27,228
ongevendt dem blitskrig.

359
00:20:27,228 --> 00:20:30,218
di daytshn zenen geganen zeyer shnel foroys.

360
00:20:30,218 --> 00:20:33,463
iz oyfn zibetn tog

361
00:20:33,463 --> 00:20:36,907
farlozt di poylishe regirung Varshe.

362
00:20:36,907 --> 00:20:39,444
tsit zikh ariber keyn Lublin.

363
00:20:39,444 --> 00:20:41,629
in dem zelbn tog

364
00:20:41,629 --> 00:20:46,999
bet di poylishe regirung az ale mener

365
00:20:46,999 --> 00:20:51,092
zoln zikh a- aveklozn oyf mizrekh un oyf dorem,

366
00:20:51,092 --> 00:20:58,388
kedey tsu zayn, azoy tsu zogn, der rezerv, vayl di daytshn derneentern zikh tsu Varshe.

367
00:20:58,388 --> 00:21:02,203
in dem tog hob ikh farlozt Varshe.

368
00:21:02,203 --> 00:21:05,666
in di ershte moment iz geven di meyn,

369
00:21:05,666 --> 00:21:09,351
kh'hob geredt mit mayne eltern,

370
00:21:09,351 --> 00:21:16,018
az mayne eltern, mayn mame shtamt fun di gegnt fun Zhelekhov, ariberforn dem klenern shtetl

371
00:21:16,018 --> 00:21:21,017
vu s'iz ruiker, me ken efsher beser bahaltn di milkhome.

372
00:21:21,017 --> 00:21:25,970
hot, der tate hot mir gants ofn gezogt, s- mir hobn shoyn ibergelebt

373
00:21:25,970 --> 00:21:31,406
di ershte velt-milkhome, mit di daytshn, zenen nisht oyf azoy fil shreklekh

374
00:21:31,406 --> 00:21:33,925
vi me meynt, mir'n blaybn in Varshe.

375
00:21:33,925 --> 00:21:36,361
ir kinder, ets vilt geyn, geyt.

376
00:21:37,840 --> 00:21:40,436
un avek fun Varshe bin ikh mit nokh a bruder.

377
00:21:41,259 --> 00:21:43,408
di reshte zaynen geblibn in Varshe?

378
00:21:43,296 --> 00:21:44,944
NO.

379
00:21:44,944 --> 00:21:48,184
 nokh tsvey brider zenen avek

380
00:21:48,184 --> 00:21:50,833
un der khasene gehater bruder,

381
00:21:50,833 --> 00:21:54,018
geven mit a pitsl kind, iz er nisht avek.

382
00:21:54,018 --> 00:21:58,296
merstn teyl, di greste, zol ikh zogn azoy,

383
00:21:58,296 --> 00:22:04,944
ikh mit eyn bruder, shpeter der driter, iz yeder eyner, vil ikh zogn azoy, m'iz nisht geganen loyt de- a geshlosene...

384
00:22:04,944 --> 00:22:06,864
ale brider in eynem.

385
00:22:08,259 --> 00:22:13,723
iz baym aroysgeyn fun Varshe bin ikh geganen mitn eltern, mit a eltern bruder, Yosl.

386
00:22:14,957 --> 00:22:17,999
un az m'iz tsugekumen

387
00:22:17,999 --> 00:22:19,537
bay Alt-Milosne

388
00:22:19,537 --> 00:22:22,946
vu der veg geyt avek oyf dorem keyn Lublin,

389
00:22:22,946 --> 00:22:26,295
un geyt avek oyf Shedlits, keyn Brisk, oyf mizrekh,

390
00:22:26,295 --> 00:22:32,703
hot men zikh tsekusht un nokh funandergeganen. vayl ikh hob in Lublin gedarft trefn

391
00:22:32,703 --> 00:22:36,481
di ale mitarbeter fun di shul-organizatsye in Varshe.

392
00:22:36,667 --> 00:22:39,119
vos zaynen shoyn oykhet gehat avekgef-

393
00:22:38,055 --> 00:22:39,295
avek, avek.

394
00:22:39,295 --> 00:22:43,277
 iz ver avekgeganen oyf links, ikh bin mir avekgeganen.

395
00:22:43,277 --> 00:22:45,110
dos iz geven der letster tog.

396
00:22:45,110 --> 00:22:49,267
avek, geyendik O mit vos, ir zayt geforn oder...

397
00:22:47,721 --> 00:22:49,407
oh!

398
00:22:49,407 --> 00:22:52,074
 tsu geyn

399
00:22:52,074 --> 00:22:53,788
vi azoy iz es

400
00:22:53,037 --> 00:22:55,149
 dem merstn teyl geganen tsu fus.

401
00:22:55,149 --> 00:22:55,851
tsu fus.

402
00:22:55,294 --> 00:23:00,516
ober me hot genitst ale meglekhe komunikatsye-mitlen vi azoy eyner hot gekent.

403
00:23:00,629 --> 00:23:04,222
mayn spetsyalitet iz geven zikh nokhhengen

404
00:23:04,222 --> 00:23:07,425
oyf durkhforndike oytos.

405
00:23:07,425 --> 00:23:13,166
vartn oyf an oysboyg fun veg, der oyto muz say vi say farklenern de- dem loyf,

406
00:23:13,166 --> 00:23:14,684
aroyfshpringen.

407
00:23:14,684 --> 00:23:17,721
dos iz geven di gimnastik

408
00:23:17,721 --> 00:23:21,240
fun di Varshever yinglekh, yidishe yinglekh,

409
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:24,166
fun nokhloyfn, zikh aroyfkhapn in tramvay,

410
00:23:24,166 --> 00:23:29,092
in fuln gang, un aroysshpringen fun tramvay in fuln gang.

411
00:23:29,092 --> 00:23:31,981
ober ikh hob es gemakht zeyer shnel.

412
00:23:31,981 --> 00:23:35,915
zaynen oyfn veg, zaynen geven a sakh mentshn vos zaynen gegangen tsu fus?

413
00:23:34,796 --> 00:23:38,282
oh, tsu toyznt

414
00:23:38,282 --> 00:23:42,487
tsu toyznter mentshn. tsu dem iz nokh tsugekumen vos di daytshe avyonen

415
00:23:42,487 --> 00:23:46,629
flegn zikh aroplozn bashisn mit mashin-gever

416
00:23:46,629 --> 00:23:50,294
di geyendike mase fun mentshn.

417
00:23:50,294 --> 00:23:56,451
der bruder vos iz avek oyfn veg keyn Shedlits hot im farkhapt di bombardirung fun Shedlits,

418
00:23:56,451 --> 00:23:59,098
iz er tsurikgeganen keyn Varshe.

419
00:23:59,098 --> 00:24:01,777
mir hot farkhapt aza bombardirung

420
00:24:01,777 --> 00:24:03,574
oyfn veg keyn Lublin,

421
00:24:03,574 --> 00:24:08,092
iz geven a shtetl, a yidish shtetl oyfn veg, Garvolin.

422
00:24:08,092 --> 00:24:11,239
geven fun beyde zaytn shosey.

423
00:24:11,239 --> 00:24:14,665
iz dos gantse shtetl gevorn farbrent un bombardirt.

424
00:24:14,665 --> 00:24:18,813
azoy hot der veg oyf Lublin zikh opgehakt, hot men gedarft geyn arum un arum.

425
00:24:18,813 --> 00:24:22,980
un aroyskumen vider oyfn Lubliner veg.

426
00:24:22,980 --> 00:24:26,054
az kh'bin arayn in Lublin,

427
00:24:26,423 --> 00:24:27,809
kh'hob dortn gehat a khaver

428
00:24:27,809 --> 00:24:32,962
vos er hot zikh aribergetsoygn, di eltern hobn zikh aribergetsoygn keyn Lublin.

429
00:24:32,962 --> 00:24:36,203
un fun tsveytn tog vert bombardirt Lublin.

430
00:24:36,203 --> 00:24:38,970
a shoyderlekhe bombardirung.

431
00:24:40,943 --> 00:24:43,517
kh'hob shoyn gezen az s'iz shoyn

432
00:24:43,517 --> 00:24:46,480
bombardir-, Lublin iz shoyn oykhet bombardirt.

433
00:24:46,480 --> 00:24:50,206
zikh ⟨barekhnt⟩ ikh vel oykhet geyn, geyn vayter.

434
00:24:50,206 --> 00:24:52,877
un der tsil iz geven tsu dergreykhn

435
00:24:52,877 --> 00:24:57,163
di sovyetishe grenets. di sovyetishe oder di rumenishe grenets.

436
00:24:59,611 --> 00:25:03,703
iz aroysgeyn fun Lublin durkh Khelm

437
00:25:03,703 --> 00:25:07,900
un do vil ikh batseykhenen, ikh bin arayngekumen in a kleyn shtetl,

438
00:25:07,900 --> 00:25:09,195
far Kovel,

439
00:25:10,751 --> 00:25:12,268
vegn di...

440
00:25:11,935 --> 00:25:12,857
far Kovel?

441
00:25:12,741 --> 00:25:13,997
far Kovel.

442
00:25:14,423 --> 00:25:17,254
iz, vegn di solidaritet

443
00:25:18,499 --> 00:25:21,592
fun di yidishe bafelkerung tsu di pleytim

444
00:25:21,592 --> 00:25:24,636
vos flegn loyfn fun Varshe un fun andere un dos...

445
00:25:26,317 --> 00:25:27,554
iz,

446
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:33,728
vi geyt, vi kumt men aroys, dos ershte, ale shtetlekh iz

447
00:25:33,728 --> 00:25:38,590
di geboy fun di shtetlekh, iz geven der mark, un arum dem mark

448
00:25:38,590 --> 00:25:40,409
geslekh un gasn.

449
00:25:40,409 --> 00:25:44,325
az me kumt arayn in shtetl, iz dos ershte geyt men aroys oyfn mark,

450
00:25:44,325 --> 00:25:46,759
oder me zukht a besmedresh.

451
00:25:46,759 --> 00:25:48,838
bin ikh ongekumen in dem shtetl

452
00:25:48,838 --> 00:25:51,036
MACIEJÓW.

453
00:25:51,036 --> 00:25:57,221
shtey ikh azoy, vi me zogt, azoy vi, shtey ikh in mark. geyt adurkh a yunger, a yunger bokher.

454
00:25:57,221 --> 00:26:00,648
kukt mikh on. in di provintsn zenen merstn teyl geven shemevdike.

455
00:26:01,425 --> 00:26:05,277
kukt mikh on, geyt vayter, ober ikh ze er dreyt zikh oys

456
00:26:05,277 --> 00:26:08,185
un kukt mikh on. ikh hob nisht bamerkt,

457
00:26:08,185 --> 00:26:12,462
ale organizatsyes hobn gegat zhetonen, optseykhenungen.

458
00:26:12,462 --> 00:26:15,257
az ikh hob nokh getrogn dem zheton fun der Tsukunft.

459
00:26:15,257 --> 00:26:18,465
fun yugnt-bund Tsukunft in lats.

460
00:26:18,465 --> 00:26:21,037
kumt er tsu un fregt mir

461
00:26:21,037 --> 00:26:23,740
"du bist a tsukunftist?" zog ikh "yo."

462
00:26:23,740 --> 00:26:28,685
"fun vanen veyst ir?" zogt er "vayl ikh ze host dem zheton in lats." a!

463
00:26:28,685 --> 00:26:32,407
arayngefirt tsvishn di bundishe grupe,

464
00:26:32,407 --> 00:26:35,351
un me hot mikh bald bashtat mit a voynung,

465
00:26:35,351 --> 00:26:39,486
dos heyst, genumen an oyrekh oyf shabes.

466
00:26:39,486 --> 00:26:45,350
un dort bin ikh opgeven, mikh opgerut, ⟨ikh vel dir zogn azoy⟩ a dray teg.

467
00:26:45,350 --> 00:26:49,487
ober di daytshn zenen shoyn ariber di Vaysl

468
00:26:49,487 --> 00:26:53,500
un zey hobn zikh genumen derneentern

469
00:26:53,703 --> 00:26:57,326
tsu Lublin, di dorem-gegntn fun Poyln.

470
00:27:00,115 --> 00:27:03,031
kh'hob mikh oyfgehoybn, vayter geganen.

471
00:27:03,076 --> 00:27:07,703
un di iberike, di iberike, di iberike mentshn zaynen geblibn oyfn ort?

472
00:27:03,202 --> 00:27:04,942
un azoy durkh...?

473
00:27:07,703 --> 00:27:09,833
di greste teyl iz geblibn oyfn ort.

474
00:27:09,833 --> 00:27:15,036
zey hobn, in di kleyne shtetlekh hot men zeyer vintsik zikh ge-

475
00:27:15,036 --> 00:27:18,851
geyogt zikh farlozn dos ort.

476
00:27:18,851 --> 00:27:20,925
azoy durkh Kovel,

477
00:27:20,925 --> 00:27:22,596
fun Kovel

478
00:27:23,984 --> 00:27:26,154
hob ikh mikh derneentert tsu Lutsk.

479
00:27:27,073 --> 00:27:29,666
ven, fun farn ⟨a⟩ onkumen keyn Lutsk

480
00:27:29,666 --> 00:27:31,888
iz shoyn di royte armey

481
00:27:31,888 --> 00:27:34,925
aribergeganen di alte poylishe gebitn.

482
00:27:34,925 --> 00:27:38,185
un ongehoybn tsu, vi ir vilt zikh oysdrikn,

483
00:27:38,185 --> 00:27:40,761
tsi bafrayen mayrev-Ukraine,

484
00:27:40,761 --> 00:27:43,796
tsi okupirn halb Poyln.

485
00:27:43,796 --> 00:27:44,792
avade.

486
00:27:44,792 --> 00:27:50,633
ven me hot derzen di ershte rusishe tanken mit di royte fener

487
00:27:50,633 --> 00:27:55,351
un nokh dertsu di ale, vi kritish me zol nisht hobn geven tsum komunizm

488
00:27:55,351 --> 00:27:57,017
iz Sovyet-Rusland

489
00:27:57,017 --> 00:27:59,487
geven azoy tsu zogn der,

490
00:27:59,487 --> 00:28:01,716
dos land vu s'geyt oyf a naye zun,

491
00:28:01,716 --> 00:28:03,816
a naye zun.

492
00:28:03,816 --> 00:28:07,091
vu es vert geshafn a nayer sovyetisher mentsh.

493
00:28:07,091 --> 00:28:10,684
ober me hot nisht gedoyert lang, hot men zikh arumgekukt

494
00:28:10,684 --> 00:28:12,758
az der nayer sovyetisher mentsh

495
00:28:12,758 --> 00:28:17,425
iz der zelber alter mentsh mit ale meglekhe felern un khesroynes.

